<h1 style="margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 22px; color: #183c67;">You've been invited to <%= @account.name %></h1>

<p style="margin: 0 0 16px;"><%= @inviter.name %> has invited you to join <strong><%= @account.name %></strong> on insAIght Hub.</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 24px;">insAIght Hub helps teams extract insights from documents using AI-powered analysis.</p>

<table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 0 0 24px;">
  <tr>
    <td style="background-color: #33b8ed; border-radius: 6px;">
      <%= link_to "Accept Invitation", register_url(token: @invite.token), style: "display: inline-block; padding: 14px 32px; color: #ffffff; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;" %>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style="margin: 0 0 8px; color: #888888; font-size: 14px;">This invitation will expire on <%= @invite.expires_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %>.</p>

<p style="margin: 0; color: #888888; font-size: 14px;">If you weren't expecting this invitation, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
